{"id": 1796, "genre": 1000, "title": "经过多年洗礼，哪些“王婆式宣传套路”你早已烂熟于心？", "description": "流行丧和自嘲的年代，还有人在坚守这种原始的营销方式。（题图来自Pixabay)", "record_count": 12864, "comment_count": 16, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170711140255BEVTLCOpg2mR718k.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-07-19T17:00:40Z", "questions": [{"id": 2588, "title": "经过多年洗礼，哪些“王婆式宣传套路”你早已烂熟于心？", "content": "经过多年洗礼，哪些“王婆式宣传套路”你早已烂熟于心？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 220587, "content": "流量钓鱼：比如“限量发售”早晚会复刻成为常态款", "image": "img/option/option/20170711140609Hd8XWgLONjSD7AZ0.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 220593, "content": "自抬身价：网红食品实名制认证购买，制造一种我卖的是御膳的幻觉", "image": "img/option/option/20170711141120eXrwzvnULQNY7s3c.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 220592, "content": "国际气质的文案：“全球每秒售出1瓶”、“加起来绕地球一圈”", "image": "img/option/option/20170711141040vGr3inwDQMk24gpJ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 220591, "content": "一词多义：比如公司架构扁平的意思是你要同时做公关/销售/行政", "image": "img/option/option/20170711141011YSt5PJB0ZlhpULXv.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 220590, "content": "流氓型自圆其说：草莓没熟发白的一定就是新品种奶油草莓", "image": "img/option/option/20170711140940ViXQFatIL2YvRDnf.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 220589, "content": "饥饿营销：你手上这是全宇宙最后一个了，哪儿哪儿都缺货", "image": "img/option/option/20170711140714OMVQpyWZiIHe1u6G.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 220588, "content": "伪科学：换了套新护肤品，爆痘过敏成鬼，商家告诉你这是在排毒", "image": "img/option/option/20170711140649DzrJaAyqM8c0LIZg.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 220594, "content": "理直气壮的骗术：任何“产品以实物为准”的广告", "image": "img/option/option/20170711141157Aq6auDmY7OKltGpC.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}